---
title: Colorful Confetti Salad with Corn, Beans, Feta, and Cajun Spices
description: One of the simplest ways to eat well is by incorporating fruits and veggies of every stripe and shade into your diet. In that spirit, we’ve got a salad that’s exploding with color: there’s brilliant orange sweet potatoes, blushing red tomatoes, and even some verdant green from lime and parsley. Altogether, it’s as nourishing and wholesome as it is delightful and satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/au-cuban-confetti-salad-w06-0c618dad.jpg
